---
interface Props {
  lang: 'ja' | 'en';
}

const { lang } = Astro.props;
const isEn = lang === 'en';

const items = isEn
  ? [
      'What stays in memory is not information on a screen, but experiences that actually happened.',
      'Encounters, change, results — none of them are born inside a screen.',
      'Technology\'s role is not to bind people to screens, but to push them into reality.',
    ]
  : [
      '人の記憶に残るのは、画面の中の情報ではなく、現実で起きた体験である。',
      '出会いも、変化も、成果も——リアルでしか生まれない。',
      'テクノロジーの役割は、人を画面に縛ることではなく、現実へ押し出すこと。',
    ];
---

<section class="section section--dark" id="philosophy">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="section-label-line">
      <span class="section-label">Philosophy</span>
    </div>
    <div class="section-grid">
      <div>
        <h2 class="philosophy-heading fade-up">
          {isEn ? (
            <>Life happens<br />beyond the screen.</>
          ) : (
            <>人生は、<br />画面の外で動いている。</>
          )}
        </h2>
        <p class="section-body">
          {isEn
            ? 'Technology has evolved to compete for people\'s attention inside screens. Yet the encounters that stay with us, the changes in our bodies, and the experiences that move our lives — all of them happen beyond the screen.'
            : 'テクノロジーは、人の可処分時間を画面の中で奪い合うために進化してきた。しかし、記憶に残る出会いも、身体の変化も、人生を動かす体験も——すべては画面の外で起きている。'}
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="philosophy-statements">
          {items.map((text, i) => (
            <div class="philosophy-item">
              <span class="philosophy-num">{String(i + 1).padStart(2, '0')}</span>
              <p class="philosophy-text">{text}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
        <a href="#concept" class="btn-pill btn-pill--white">
          Concept <span class="arrow">&gt;</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
